%N A025998 Expansion of 1/((1-2*x)*(1-5*x)*(1-8*x)*(1-10*x)).
%H A025998 Vincenzo Librandi, <a href="/A025998/b025998.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..900</a>
%H A025998 <a href="/index/Rec#order_04">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (25,-216,740,-800).
%F A025998 a(n) = -2^n/18+25*5^n/9-128*8^n/9+25*10^n/2. - _R. J. Mathar_, Jun 20 2013
%F A025998 a(n) = 25*a(n-1)-216*a(n-2)+740*a(n-3)-800*a(n-4), with a(0)=1, a(1)=25, a(2)=409, a(3)=5565. - _Harvey P. Dale_, Aug 25 2014
%F A025998 a(n) = (5^(n+1)-2^(n+1))/3+18*a(n-1)-80*a(n-2). - _Vincenzo Librandi_, Jul 11 2026
%t A025998 CoefficientList[Series[1/((1-2x)(1-5x)(1-8x)(1-10x)),{x,0,20}],x] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Aug 25 2014 *)
